description: Concerns have been raised in Jersey after the Channel Islands agreed to be part of the UK/EU deal.
title: Jersey fishermen 'not celebrating' Brexit deal
title_page: Jersey fishermen 'not celebrating' Brexit deal - BBC News
maintext: That treaty had been accused of unfairly favouring France as it allowed French authorities to license their own boats to fish in Jersey waters, and the French fleet has hundreds of vessels, compared to Jersey's 75.
